::KitKat::

Sees how Cyber Claw isn't the most socialable bot.  But notices how 
she shows her feelings on the outside.  Knows that Cyber Claw is 
extremely unhappy with what is going on just by body language.  She 
moves to the end of the table and offers Cyber Claw the plush, 
captain's chair. "Please, make yourself comfortable." she said in a 
soft and warm voice.
